CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Office of the Deaf and Hard of Hearing and Maryland Advisory Council on Deaf
3 and Hard of Hearing – Renaming
4 FOR the purpose of renaming the Office of the Deaf and Hard of Hearing to be the Office
5 of the Deaf, Deafblind, and Hard of Hearing; renaming the Maryland Advisory
6 Council on Deaf and Hard of Hearing to be the Maryland Advisory Council on Deaf,
7 Deafblind, and Hard of Hearing; and generally relating to renaming the Office of the
8 Deaf and Hard of Hearing and the Maryland Advisory Council on Deaf and Hard of
9 Hearing.
